name: Mysterious GalNet Crate II
description: Part of a deal with Paragon, this crate was en route to a GalNet Streamcast Unit when it disappeared. Once lost, now recovered, it is yours for the taking. Upon opening, you will receive Agency Support Drop plus one of the following: a random GalNet StreamCast Unit SKIN 19th Tier Overseer's Personal Effects 23rd Tier Overseer's Personal Effects PLEX
